Output assets/twitter.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1000
Set Height 500
Set Theme "TokyoNight"
Set TypingSpeed 35ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.2

Type "# Multiple Claude Code agents. One debate."
Sleep 700ms
Enter
Sleep 400ms

Type "npx roundtable debate --topic 'Monorepo vs polyrepo?'"
Sleep 600ms
Enter

Sleep 12s
